      <questionContent>
        <question eId="q_1">
          <p>What share of the 2024 culinary budget was allocated to saffron procurement for the preparation of official events?</p>
        </question>
        <question eId="q_2">
          <p>Does the Ministry plan to update the saffron guidance in the <ref href="/akn/poc/act/valencian-paella-recipe">Official Valencian Paella Recipe Act</ref> to reflect the current market price?</p>
        </question>
      </questionContent>

      <answerContent>
        <p>The Ministry allocated 12% of the 2024 culinary budget to certified saffron purchases, prioritizing local suppliers.</p>
        <p>No amendment to the act is planned for the current session, but a review will be considered after the 2024 harvest cycle.</p>
      </answerContent>
